<section name="132" image="132.jpg">
	<p>
		It is with mounting excitement that you recognize this island as the one marked on the map.
	</p>
	<p>
		Digging at the spot marked, you find a chest containing a handsome haul.
	</p>
	<p><random dice="1"/> to see what it is.</p>
	<outcomes>
		<outcome range="1">
			<gain shards="100"/> and a
			<weapon name="sword" bonus="3"/>
		</outcome>
		<outcome range="2">
			<gain shards="400"/> and a
			<tool name="compass" ability="scouting" bonus="1"/>
		</outcome>
		<outcome range="3">
			<gain shards="200"/> and
			<armour name="plate armour" bonus="5"/>
		</outcome>
		<outcome range="4">
			<gain shards="300"/> and an
			<tool name="ebony wand" ability="magic" bonus="2"/>
		</outcome>
		<outcome range="5">
			<gain shards="1000"/> and a <item name="candle"/>
		</outcome>
		<outcome range="6">
			<gain shards="200"/> and a
			<item name="pirate captain's head"><b>pirate captain&#8217;s head</b></item>
		</outcome>
	</outcomes>
	<p>
		When you have recorded the details of your treasure on your Adventure Sheet, cross off the <lose item="treasure map" group="3.94"/> and <goto section="150"/>.
	</p>
</section>
